_section][vc_section css=".vc_custom_1499871823132{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Core Values" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:68|text_align:left|line_height:1.2" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="section-title line left" css=".vc_custom_1499870508008{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="189" img_size="full" el_class="content"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="190" img_size="full" el_class="content"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We value people" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]<p>We believe there is innate value in all people. We act in ways that respect the dignity, uniqueness, and intrinsic worth of every person and celebrate the richness of diversity in human personality, experience, culture, and contribution. We actively seek the best for all people, those who work with us, our clients, partners, their families, and communities, here and across the globe. We practice an open, participative, collaborative, uplifting and empowering style in working relationships. We encourage the professional, personal, and spiritual development of our staff.</p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We change the world for the better" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]<p>We proudly support and empower mission-serving organizations and individuals who have chosen to devote their life’s work to improve our world. We seek to multiply their work every day by providing unparalleled partnership support and high-quality, exceptional service to our clients’ mission and by encouraging this same attitude of service in our business partners, vendors, and coworkers.</p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We are entrepreneurs" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]<p>We continuously seek opportunities to evolve, innovate and improve in all aspects of our work, from the strategies and services we offer our clients to the way we approach our jobs. We take risks because we want to be great, not simply good. We are leaders who accept personal responsibility for our commitments, our work, and our relationships. We challenge prevailing assumptions, create new ideas, and discover practical solutions and we are open to change.</p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We have fun and celebrate creativity" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]<p>It’s no secret . . . we’re a little “out of the box.” And we’re good with that. Having fun and celebrating unique individual and team talents empower creativity and enhance problem-solving, making us better as people and as an agency.</p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We encourage balance and we give back" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]<p>We are a work hard - play hard group. But while we revel in our work and play to win, we also strongly encourage a perspective that values balance, particularly between work and family. This same perspective motivates a company-wide desire to help those less fortunate, to give back.</p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section css=".vc_custom_1499872598868{padding-top: 35px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #f3f3f3 !important;}"][vc_row el_class="container" css=".vc_custom_1499874503875{margin-bottom: 26px !important;}"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="Core Values" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:68|text_align:left|line_height:1.2" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="section-title line left"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="We’re always looking for great talent." font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="careers-sub-title " css=".vc_custom_1499874542162{margin-bottom: 22px !important;}"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]<p>The Lukens Company is a dynamic, growing organization and we are always looking for qualified individuals to become new members of our team. We invite you to submit your resume by clicking on the link below and will contact you should your experience meet our current needs.</p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1499872758454{padding-left: 100px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Current Positions" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left|color:%23c47013" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="careers-sub-title " css=".vc_custom_1499874555790{margin-bottom: 22px !important;}"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]<p>Position #1<br />\nPosition #2<br />\nPosition #3</p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section]";}s:26:"lukens-services-list_17381";a:2:{s:4:"name";s:22:"Lukens "Services List"";s:8:"template";s:9375:"[vc_section][vc_row full_height="yes" equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="137" img_size="444x296" alignment="right" onclick="custom_link" link="/service/direct-marketing-fundraising" el_class="content"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1499890255136{padding-top: 158px !important;padding-bottom: 110px !impo