 world. We seek to multiply their work every day by providing unparalleled partnership support and high-quality, exceptional service to our clients’ mission and by encouraging this same attitude of service in our business partners, vendors, and coworkers.</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We are entrepreneurs" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]</p>\r\n<p>We continuously seek opportunities to evolve, innovate and improve in all aspects of our work, from the strategies and services we offer our clients to the way we approach our jobs. We take risks because we want to be great, not simply good. We are leaders who accept personal responsibility for our commitments, our work, and our relationships. We challenge prevailing assumptions, create new ideas, and discover practical solutions and we are open to change.</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We have fun and celebrate creativity" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]</p>\r\n<p>It’s no secret . . . we’re a little “out of the box.” And we’re good with that. Having fun and celebrating unique individual and team talents empower creativity and enhance problem-solving, making us better as people and as an agency.</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="We encourage balance and we give back" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="person-name"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]</p>\r\n<p>We are a work hard - play hard group. But while we revel in our work and play to win, we also strongly encourage a perspective that values balance, particularly between work and family. This same perspective motivates a company-wide desire to help those less fortunate, to give back.</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section css=".vc_custom_1499872598868{padding-top: 35px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #f3f3f3 !important;}"][vc_row el_class="container" css=".vc_custom_1499874503875{margin-bottom: 26px !important;}"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="Core Values" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:68|text_align:left|line_height:1.2" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="section-title line left"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="container"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="We’re always looking for great talent." font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="careers-sub-title " css=".vc_custom_1499874542162{margin-bottom: 22px !important;}"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]</p>\r\n<p>The Lukens Company is a dynamic, growing organization and we are always looking for qualified individuals to become new members of our team. We invite you to submit your resume by clicking on the link below and will contact you should your experience meet our current needs.</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1499872758454{padding-left: 100px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Current Positions" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:31|text_align:left|color:%23c47013" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="careers-sub-title " css=".vc_custom_1499874555790{margin-bottom: 22px !important;}"][vc_column_text el_class="content"]</p>\r\n<p>Position #1<br />\r\n Position #2<br />\r\n Position #3</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section]</p>', 'Leadership', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-14 06:52:48', '2017-07-14 11:52:48', '', 14, 'http://sham.esy.es/uncategorized/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
